01:05:16.388 --> 01:05:23.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But to have your love forever
Is a real and lasting treasure.

01:05:23.479 --> 01:05:35.950 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You alone will prove to be
Our joy eternally.

01:05:43.332 --> 01:05:47.795 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
After that touching video,
what more is there to say?

01:05:47.795 --> 01:05:51.340 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Find your greatest joy” in Jehovah.

01:05:51.340 --> 01:05:53.342 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Rejoice!

01:05:53.342 --> 01:05:55.928 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our deliverance is near.

01:05:56.888 --> 01:05:58.890 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Thank you, Brother Splane.

01:05:58.890 --> 01:06:02.310 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Your talk and this entire convention

01:06:02.310 --> 01:06:06.981 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
